# The knowledge graph itself IS committed (graph.json, graph.html, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# manifest.json, cost.json, cache/) — see ../CLAUDE.md. Only machine-specific or
# regenerated sidecars are ignored so the committed graph stays portable.

# Absolute, per-machine pointers written on each run
.graphify_python
.graphify_root

# Internal labeling sidecar — regenerated every build
.graphify_labels.json

# Transient per-build temp files (normally auto-cleaned)
.graphify_detect.*
.graphify_*.tmp
.needs_update

# Machine-specific file-stat index for --update change detection (regenerated)
cache/stat-index.json
